Initial Setup
=============

After cheking out, please do the following steps:

1) generate/update the list of plugins by running
$ tools/mksbt.sh

2) create eclipse projects for all plugins by running
$ tools/mkeclipse

3) setup git by running
$ cat > .git/hooks/pre-commit
#!/bin/bash

set -e
tools/spaces.sh --git
^D
$ chmod 755 .git/hooks/pre-commit

4) Test everything by running
$ tools/run.sh
and
$tools/mkdist.sh
